{"tid":1353842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"出道3年連1天都沒有休息過！請夏讀觀眾來信無預警淚崩","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T22:50:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd1ef1d50902e99dc8b7697fb97fd113e6f67fb","tid":1353842,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_297dbe546128d9a92ce169b0c0b858c3/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-07-22/118637-755439.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_297dbe546128d9a92ce169b0c0b858c3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-07-22%2F118637-755439.png&h=dc108c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好心疼請夏T^T 雖然高頻度的回歸讓粉絲幸福感滿滿，但也希望請夏不要過度疲勞，至少在I.O.I重組的忙碌期之前犒勞一下自己吧......<br />\n<br />\n本月16日請夏出演《I&rsquo;m Celuv》時被問到休息時喜歡做什麼，回答：「沒有什麼說得上是休息的時間。 沒有日程的時候就上課、為舞台表演做準備，時間都安排得滿滿的。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2b0d9e2e71e13fd5db69ed830dfbd8d7/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-07-22/118637-755430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2b0d9e2e71e13fd5db69ed830dfbd8d7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-07-22%2F118637-755430.png&h=1d0fd9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMC問她如果有2周的休息時間想用來做什麼，請夏聽後微微一笑：「我有自信什麼都不做。 如果有『什麼都不做世界大賽』的話，我有自信拿到第一名。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8b802a64a12dea1d4262b84d1797efe2/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-07-22/118637-755433.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8b802a64a12dea1d4262b84d1797efe2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-07-22%2F118637-755433.png&h=40a40fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來，請夏自從2016年通過Ment《Produce 101》出道之後的3年來，一直在努力工作，幾乎不曾有過休息的時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c14ca26c958e906438ced5ed7eb58442/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-07-22/118637-755434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c14ca26c958e906438ced5ed7eb58442%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-07-22%2F118637-755434.jpg&h=09c28858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21日請夏出演EBS電臺節目《請夏的傾聽》，讀到一則聽眾留言時突然淚流滿面。 這位聽眾說：「請夏大人，您辛苦了，要保重健康哦。 」請夏聞言一時說不出話來，隨後用手捂住了臉......<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_46082b64367ed9d671cf1fa240fa0022/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-07-22/118637-755438.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_46082b64367ed9d671cf1fa240fa0022%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-07-22%2F118637-755438.jpg&h=42f60b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好不容易恢復一點平靜之後，請夏艱難地說：「我沒關係。 」但還是不斷哽咽，MC於是很有sense地進了一段音樂，給請夏一些時間整理情緒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/moonoom_moon/status/1153106716227072000?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1153106716227072000&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F118637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmoonoom_moon%2Fstatus%2F1153106716227072000%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1153106716227072000%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.koreastardaily.com%252Ftc%252Fnews%252F118637&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUioL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1605552c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmoonoom_moon%2Fstatus%2F1153106716227072000%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1153106716227072000%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.koreastardaily.com%252Ftc%252Fnews%252F118637&h=0af63551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/moonoom_moon/status/1153106716227072000?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1153106716227072000&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F118637</a>"},{"pid":"419316724eea45cf401d552a4dc96a2d7e87aaa7","tid":1353842,"uid":76632,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"我Roller Coaster請夏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":